Already?

394
00:34:21,937 --> 00:34:27,035
Yes, we'll release new menus
next week with publicity.

395
00:34:27,570 --> 00:34:30,034
You look full of confidence.

396
00:34:30,035 --> 00:34:33,402
Seems Lena acts her part well.

397
00:34:33,403 --> 00:34:34,736
I feel reassured.

398
00:34:34,737 --> 00:34:36,034
If this new menus make a hit,

399
00:34:36,035 --> 00:34:38,302
we can push into
Shanghai right away.

400
00:34:38,303 --> 00:34:39,369
Maybe next month...

401
00:34:39,370 --> 00:34:40,370
Minjoon.

402
00:34:43,103 --> 00:34:48,035
Actually, I called you in
regarding that matter.

403
00:34:49,169 --> 00:34:54,035
How about putting it off?

404
00:34:55,570 --> 00:34:58,636
Things are messed up.

405
00:34:58,637 --> 00:35:00,502
Your business expansion...

406
00:35:00,503 --> 00:35:03,903
and Jaejoon's marriage
came up all at once...

407
00:35:03,904 --> 00:35:06,035
and it's beyond my limit.

408
00:35:07,035 --> 00:35:09,369
Though I have money to burn,

409
00:35:09,370 --> 00:35:14,035
it's too much for me
to support you both.

410
00:35:14,803 --> 00:35:15,203
So...

411
00:35:15,204 --> 00:35:17,035
I see your point.

412
00:35:19,035 --> 00:35:20,703
Support Jaejoon first.

413
00:35:21,703 --> 00:35:23,335
I think Stepmother
wishes it too,

414
00:35:23,336 --> 00:35:25,569
though she didn't show it.

415
00:35:25,570 --> 00:35:30,034
Well, it's not
because she wishes it...

416
00:35:30,035 --> 00:35:33,035
As long as
you are happy, I'm fine.

417
00:35:36,035 --> 00:35:39,203
Well, I'm really sorry.

418
00:35:40,035 --> 00:35:42,035
I'll get back to work.

419
00:35:50,970 --> 00:35:54,870
That's my boy.
Very thoughtful.

420
00:35:56,436 --> 00:35:58,436
That's why I trust him.

421
00:36:10,236 --> 00:36:14,469
