457
00:38:06,103 --> 00:38:11,603
I clearly told you to
keep this matter between us.

458
00:38:12,069 --> 00:38:16,034
Don't worry, Mrs. Park.
My mouth is tight.

459
00:38:16,035 --> 00:38:18,836
I initiate contact with you.

460
00:38:18,837 --> 00:38:23,836
So don't make a call to me.
Understood?

461
00:38:23,837 --> 00:38:26,035
Okay. I'm sorry.

462
00:38:27,035 --> 00:38:29,035
Lena Jeong will be on a roll?

463
00:38:30,035 --> 00:38:32,035
Don't make me laugh.

464
