I can finish her today.

466
00:38:43,436 --> 00:38:45,034
How are you, sir?

467
00:38:45,035 --> 00:38:46,102
Is it ready?

468
00:38:46,103 --> 00:38:48,035
Yes.
Come this way please.

469
00:38:55,136 --> 00:38:57,068
- Here's the car key.
- Thanks.

470
00:38:57,069 --> 00:38:59,370
How do you like it?

471
00:39:00,035 --> 00:39:02,802
I'm busy.
Why did you bring me here?

472
00:39:02,803 --> 00:39:04,034
Can't you tell?

473
00:39:04,035 --> 00:39:07,034
I bought a new car.
Take the wheel.

474
00:39:07,035 --> 00:39:08,035
Excuse me?

475
00:39:08,803 --> 00:39:10,469
Why should I drive your car?

476
00:39:10,470 --> 00:39:12,034
What do you mean why?

477
00:39:12,035 --> 00:39:14,702
Did you forget
I drove you home several times?

478
00:39:14,703 --> 00:39:17,503
You can at least
do me this favor. Take it.

479
00:39:19,035 --> 00:39:20,435
Mr. Park.

480
00:39:20,436 --> 00:39:22,103
You said you're busy.

481
00:39:25,403 --> 00:39:27,502
The person you have dialed
is not available.

482
00:39:27,503 --> 00:39:31,637
Dang it.
Where on earth is she?

483
00:39:32,035 --> 00:39:35,570
She's worrying me too much.

484
00:39:39,035 --> 00:39:41,302
Sir, your wife is here to see you.

485
00:39:41,303 --> 00:39:43,937
What?
My wife?

486
00:39:46,370 --> 00:39:47,502
What tea would you like to...

487
00:39:47,503 --> 00:39:50,035
Just leave us alone.
Get out.

488
00:39:53,069 --> 00:39:56,502
Honey, I'm sorry.

489
00:39:56,503 --> 00:40:01,402
I'm sorry no matter what.
Just don't leave home again.

490
00:40:01,403 --> 00:40:04,336
Without you,
I couldn't focus on work,

491
00:40:04,370 --> 00:40:06,034
I couldn't sleep,

492
00:40:06,035 --> 00:40:09,035
and I couldn't even eat.

493
00:40:14,537 --> 00:40:16,035
Honey, forgive me.

494
00:40:18,035 --> 00:40:19,936
Are you still mad at me?

495
00:40:19,937 --> 00:40:24,035
What should I do
to have your forgiveness?

496
00:40:26,035 --> 00:40:28,435
Honey, I'm sorry.

497
00:40:28,436 --> 00:40:32,335
I'm really sorry, so don't cry.

498
00:40:32,336 --> 00:40:34,035
It's not that.

499
00:40:36,035 --> 00:40:38,236
I'm not crying because of you.

500
00:40:39,036 --> 00:40:42,035
I'm just disappointed in myself.

501
00:40:43,570 --> 00:40:44,570
I...

502
00:40:45,770 --> 00:40:52,203
made a resolution to love Minjoon
as my own when I married you.

503
00:40:53,770 --> 00:40:58,903
Surely, the skin
is nearer than the shirt.

504
00:40:58,904 --> 00:41:05,335
I've come to favor
Jaejoon before I realized it.

505
00:41:05,336 --> 00:41:10,034
No, it's not your fault.
That's human nature.

506
00:41:10,035 --> 00:41:11,035
No.

507
00:41:12,537 --> 00:41:15,303
I don't deserve
to be his mother.

508
00:41:16,403 --> 00:41:18,302
You were right,

509
00:41:18,303 --> 00:41:22,536
so feel free to support Minjoon first.

510
