I will build the hospital
for Jaejoon first and then...

512
00:41:28,336 --> 00:41:29,937
No, no.

513
00:41:32,004 --> 00:41:33,436
Like you said,

514
00:41:34,035 --> 00:41:37,904
Jaejoon can't gear
his ability to the job now.

515
00:41:38,570 --> 00:41:44,470
Minjoon is your successor
so please support him first.

516
00:41:46,035 --> 00:41:48,235
Okay.

517
00:41:48,236 --> 00:41:50,303
If you insist,

518
00:41:51,035 --> 00:41:56,035
